{"tid":827004,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鬼船 加洲大地震","createTime":"2018-09-18T15:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T19:28:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0beb707087a880175bc8374ee14fc7c083910b5","tid":827004,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=974c4908\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=01730491\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6c481f0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/55/Ghost_Ship_poster.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F55%2FGhost_Ship_poster.JPG&h=f86217e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/San_Andreas_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2FSan_Andreas_Poster.jpg&h=b4218845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.安東妮雅葛莎號，是1954年在熱拿亞船塢建造的巨型遊輪，裝潢設備卻極盡奢華，被喻為人類史上第一座海上皇宮。這艘海上宮殿的保險由倫敦的羅氏保險公司所承保，並於1962年5月21日在拉布拉多半島海岸外失蹤。 非常奇怪的是，它並沒有發出求救信號或跟任何船隻通話，它就這樣憑空消失得無影無蹤。從那一天起，世上每一名打撈船長以及每一位乘客的親人都在尋找它，希望『安東妮雅葛莎號』並沒有沉船。 四十年的時間很快過去，『安東妮雅葛莎號』失蹤疑雲也在人們的記憶中漸漸變得模糊...<br />\n<br />\n2.聲名狼藉的聖安德列斯斷層（San Andreas Fault）終於崩塌之後，在加州引發了9級的大地震。負責搜尋救援的直昇機駕駛員（巨石強森 飾）與他失和的妻子決定從洛杉磯往北飛向舊金山，一同搶救他們的獨生女....<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=729d0404\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c4a47eb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b96d46f8504d19702f34c79309cf20a209317f","tid":827004,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7039971bf7077d54672713d94e91e03ccd49a7b","tid":827004,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 